# Project Map — ProFit Platform

## Overview

ProFit is a gamified swimming training platform built as a multi-role SPA.

The system supports:

- training management
- gamification and competitions
- academy CRM
- analytics and reporting
- AI-assisted features

The current implementation is a frontend-first architecture using Supabase as the backend service.

---

# Core Stack

Frontend:
- React 18
- TypeScript
- Vite (SWC)
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Framer Motion

State:
- Zustand (client state)
- TanStack React Query (server state)

Backend:
- Supabase
  - Auth
  - Database
  - Realtime

Validation:
- React Hook Form
- Zod

Routing:
- React Router v6

